txt.en:
'Hoom, hum. What are you, little one? Do not tell me, hasty creature. I will find out.

   Eldest of all, the elf-children;
   Dwarf the delver, dark are his houses;
   Ent the earthborn, old as mountains;
   Man the mortal, master of horses....

'Hm, hm, hm.

   Beaver the builder, buck the leaper,
   Bear the bee-hunter, boar the fighter;
   Hound is hungry, hare is fearful...

'Hm, hm.

   Eagle in eyrie, ox in pasture,
   Hart-horn-crowned; hawk is swiftest,
   Swan the whitest, serpent coldest...

'A long list, but you do not seem to fit in anywhere!'

<rgb=#FF0000>By completing this quest, you will receive racial traits for a high level character.</rgb>

'We shall have to make a new line for you.

   Half-grown hobbits, the hole-dwellers.

'There now, hm, that seems to fit. Will you accept the gift of your peoples?'
Talk to Snowlight to receive your Racial Traits
By completing this quest, you will receive racial traits for a high level character.
